Package com.example.alimama.homescreen

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    HomeScreenContract
    This interface is the contract interface of HomeScreenActivity screen.
    HomeScreenContract.HomeScreenPresenter
    This interface should be implemented by HomeScreenActivity screen presenter class
    HomeScreenContract.HomeScreenView
    This interface should be implemented by HomeScreenActivity screen activity class
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HomeScreenActivity
    This activity is the entrance to all other screens of the applications this class implements HomeScreenContract.HomeScreenView interface to conform Model-View-Presenter design pattern No outstanding issues identified
    HomeScreenPresenter
    This class is the implementation of HomeScreenContract.HomeScreenPresenter interface it's the presenter of Home screen.
